} Your service will need to implement this trait, and your client will use this trait to talk to the service. The generated bindings can be found at out/soong/.intermediates/<path to module>/. Point out how the generated function signature, specifically the argument and return types, correspond the interface definition. String for an argument results in a different Rust type than String as a return type.

